def test_remove(self):
        one = Resource.opaque(contents={})
        two = ID_AND_CHILDREN.create_resource({"foo": "bar"})
        registry = Registry({"urn:foo": one, "urn:bar": two})
        assert registry.remove("urn:foo") == Registry({"urn:bar": two})
